						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">miau wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Glad you found it to be useful, Banshaku. It seems to translate well to 6502 ASM, but I don't claim it's the best way to do it. Anyone is welcome to modify/improve/extend the code or provide other ideas.</div>
